name: 泰拉·奥黛丽
introduction: Tayla Audrey is an actress, known for The Wheel (2019), Chloe Lives (2015) and Snap (2017)AboutActress who landed the title role in her feature film debut Chloe Lives after previously appearing in a number of shorts and commercials.Before FameShe was 5 years old when she appeared in her first musical. She was cast as a puff of cream.TriviaShe attended Centrestage Performing Arts School to take a full-time music theatre course before studying screen acting at the Film and Television Studios International.Family LifeShe has siblings named Jezza and Alex.Associated WithShe began dating actor Mitchell Hope.
